ظآزLife is full of hardshipsظآز

00:10:25.340 --> 00:10:27.480
ظآزIn dreamsظآز

00:10:28.210 --> 00:10:31.210
ظآزI become a sleeping lotusظآز

00:10:31.830 --> 00:10:34.050
ظآزBefore awakeningظآز

